description:
Based on the design of our classic Sequoia pendant, this axe-shaped cuff takes its name from the Dutch word for &ldquo;chop.&rdquo; It has a fitting title for a piece that will keep you looking seriously sharp.

 &nbsp;

 Comes in size 7 and 8 but can be stretched slightly to accommodate in-between sizes.

 &nbsp;

 NOTE: The antiquing process differs from piece to piece. The item you receive may look slightly different than what is pictured here.
